<div class="col-sm-2 sidenav">
    <img src="https://ooo.0o0.ooo/2017/05/21/592187f12feac.png" alt="logo.png" title="logo.png" class="img-responsive" />
    <br>
    <div class="panel-group text-center">
        <!-- 首页 -->
        <div class="panel panel-primary">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a href="/">首页</a>
                </h4>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- About Us -->
        <div class="panel panel-primary">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a href="#">ABOUT US</a>
                </h4>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- 作品集 -->
        <div class="panel panel-primary">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a class="text-center" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapse1" >作品集
                        <span class="caret"></span>
                    </a>
                </h4>
            </div>
            <div id="collapse1" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    <%= link_to("手绘本", products_path) %>
                </div>
                <div class="panel-body">手绘滑板</div>
                <div class="panel-body">手绘酒瓶</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- 购物车 -->
        <div class="panel panel-primary">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <!-- <a href="/carts">购物车</a> -->
                    <%= link_to carts_path do %>
                        购物车<i class="fa fa-shopping-cart"></i> ( <%= current_cart.products.count %>)
                    <% end %>
                </h4>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- 注册，登录，Admin选项 -->
        <div class="panel panel-primary">
            <% if !current_user %>
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <a class="text-center" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapse2" >SignUp | LogIn
                            <span class="caret"></span>
                        </a>
                    </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse2" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        <%= link_to("注册", new_user_registration_path) %>
                    </div>
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        <%= link_to(content_tag(:i,'登入', class: 'fa fa-sign-in'), new_user_session_path) %>
                    </div>
                </div>
            <% else %>
                <% if current_user.is_admin? %>
                    <div class="panel-heading">
                        <h4 class="panel-title">
                            <a class="text-center" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapse3" > Hi!, <%= current_user.email %>
                                <span class="caret"></span>
                            </a>
                        </h4>
                    </div>
                    <div id="collapse3" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                        <div class="panel-body">
                            <%= link_to("My orders", account_orders_path ) %>
                        </div>
                        <div class="panel-body">
                            <%= link_to("Admin 菜单", admin_products_path) %>
                        </div>
                        <div class="panel-body">
                            <%= link_to(content_tag(:i, '登出', class: 'fa fa-sign-out'), destroy_user_session_path, method: :delete) %>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                <% else %>
                    <div class="panel-heading">
                        <h4 class="panel-title">
                            <a class="text-center" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapse4" > Hi!, <%= current_user.email %>
                                <span class="caret"></span>
                            </a>
                        </h4>
                    </div>
                    <div id="collapse4" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                        <div class="panel-body">
                            <%= link_to("My orders", account_orders_path ) %>
                        </div>
                        <div class="panel-body">
                            <%= link_to(content_tag(:i, '登出', class: 'fa fa-sign-out'), destroy_user_session_path, method: :delete) %>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                <% end %>
            <% end %>
        </div>
    </div>
    <br>
    <div>
        <p>每个人都缺乏点什么，我们才会瞬间就不快乐……</p>
        <p>单纯很难，包袱很多......</p>
        <p>已经很勇敢，还是会难过......</p>
        <p>在这里，通过手绘作品的天真和纯净，您可以用另一种方式去看世界，如茶香，如诗行。</p>
        <p>今天【绘生活】就这么成立了，与您的每一次遇见，都是缘。无论缘分深浅，我们会做得更好！</p>
    </div>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
</div>
